The Supreme Council Of Kenya Muslims (SUPKEM) Leaders Have Faulted The Extension Of The Building Bridges Initiative (BBI) Taskforce Term. The Leaders Now Want President Kenyatta To Appoint A Fresh Team To Oversee The Collection Of Views On The Recommendations Made By The BBI Team Citing Possible Political Interference If The Team Is Left To Continue With The Next Phase Of Collection Of Views From The Public. President Uhuru Kenyatta And Opposition Leader Raila Odinga Extended The Term Of The BBI Taskforce Indefinitely After Meeting The Team At State House Nairobi On Wednesday.